description: Recently sold: $169,900. No question about it, this home has tremendous potential! Solid, sound & well cared for full basement rambler home situated on a nicely treed1 acre lot! Exceptional floor plan that offers 3 bedrooms on one level, generous sized rooms throughout, a very roomy main floor full bathroom, a charming eat-in kitchen with ample cabinet space, formal dining area & an abundance of windows allowing a sun-filled living space! Excellent opportunity for future entertaining where the bar/kitchenette area is already started, great storage, workshop or more in the sprawling lower level! One will enjoy the inviting rear deck, storage shed w/concrete floor & the 30x28 insulated & heated garage or should we say man cave! Don't miss out on this fantastic chance to put your sparkle inside and out of this charming home! An awesome equity builder! We look forward to your visit!
